@startuml
title UC10 - Enviar Moedas de Mérito

' Ativa as barras/caixas de duração nas lifelines
autoactivate on
skinparam SequenceLifeLineBorderColor #6B7280
skinparam SequenceLifeLineBackgroundColor #F3F4F6
skinparam sequenceActivationBorderColor #111827
skinparam sequenceActivationBackgroundColor #DDEBFF

actor Professor as P
boundary "Painel do Professor\nNext.js" as Front
control "TransacaoController\nMicronaut" as Ctrl
control "ProfessorRepository" as ProfRepo
control "AlunoRepository" as AlunoRepo
control "TransacaoRepository" as TransRepo
queue "RabbitMQ\nFila: moedas.email" as Rabbit
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

P -> Front: Seleciona aluno, valor e motivo
Front -> Front: Valida campos e saldo exibido
Front -> Ctrl: POST /transacoes\n{remetenteId,destinatarioId,valor,motivo}
Ctrl -> ProfRepo: findById(remetenteId)
ProfRepo -> DB: SELECT professor
DB --> ProfRepo: Professor
ProfRepo --> Ctrl: Professor

Ctrl -> AlunoRepo: findById(destinatarioId)
AlunoRepo -> DB: SELECT aluno
DB --> AlunoRepo: Aluno
AlunoRepo --> Ctrl: Aluno

Ctrl -> Ctrl: Verifica mesma instituição e curso
Ctrl -> Ctrl: Verifica saldo suficiente
Ctrl -> Ctrl: professor.saldoCorrente -= valor
Ctrl -> Ctrl: aluno.saldoAtual += valor
Ctrl -> ProfRepo: update(professor)
ProfRepo -> DB: UPDATE saldo professor
Ctrl -> AlunoRepo: update(aluno)
AlunoRepo -> DB: UPDATE saldo aluno
Ctrl -> TransRepo: save(transacao)
TransRepo -> DB: INSERT transacao
DB --> TransRepo: Transação salva
TransRepo --> Ctrl: Transação
Ctrl -> Rabbit: Publica EnvioMoedasEvent
Ctrl --> Front: 201 Created\n{status: sucesso}
Front -> Front: Recarrega dados
Front --> P: Toast de sucesso

@enduml
